  - m_Id: 6901402398875648
    m_Localized: PresentDashboard
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901423366201344
    m_Localized: Gunk up the works and slow your foe down.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901443050070016
    m_Localized: DoActualWork
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901477409808384
    m_Localized: EdgeCloser
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901477669855232
    m_Localized: It's a lot easier to see and hit the target when you're right beside
      them!  Buffs brawn and pluck.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901478005399552
    m_Localized: IgnoreYou
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901478160588800
    m_Localized: The most aggressive aggression is passive. Reduces nimble temporarily.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901478475161600
    m_Localized: AveragePraise
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901478634545152
    m_Localized: Heals a little more than gentle praise.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901478949117952
    m_Localized: PeckEarHoles
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901479112695808
    m_Localized: Ouch!  Causes damage and damage over time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901479427268608
    m_Localized: LoudlyProclaim
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901479586652160
    m_Localized: Unplug your EarPods and take the call live. Reduces nimble temporarily.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901479897030656
    m_Localized: PassGas
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901480215797760
    m_Localized: Preen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901480370987008
    m_Localized: These feathers look so shiny.  Heal a small amount.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901480685559808
    m_Localized: zz_TestAction
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901480844943360
    m_Localized: Test 1234
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901481163710464
    m_Localized: Working hard pays in dividends -- your foe takes damage over time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901481478283264
    m_Localized: TwiddleThumbs
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901481633472512
    m_Localized: They're doing it!  They're really doing it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901481948045312
    m_Localized: WarmMeal
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901482107428864
    m_Localized: Home cooked meal heals some amount of HP
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901482417807360
    m_Localized: Wallop
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901482572996608
    m_Localized: It's just a light wallop to a single target.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901482891763712
