    m_Localized: Very high-pitched.  Lose some pluck.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901484091334656
    m_Localized: WordsOfEncouragement
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901484191997952
    m_Localized: These kind words heal your foe
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901484397518848
    m_Localized: NerdSnipe
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901484498182144
    m_Localized: Your foe fixates.  Stops action until damage taken.  May not always
      be successful, dependent on Luck.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901484699508736
    m_Localized: Fortify
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901484795977728
    m_Localized: Yes!  Yes!  Fortify!  Stand strong!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6901485001498624
    m_Localized: GutturalMonkChant
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
